  "title": "IT Support/ Desktop Engineer",
  "description": "<p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li>Work closely with client and vendors on back-end CCTV setup.</li><li>CCTV backend router setup, knowledge of configuration of NVR, basic router configuration (Huawei), basic networking.</li><li>Email setup based on Microsoft Apps</li><li>Generate reports, maintain dashboards, workflow update, track vendor productivity, vendor system, software and hardware requisition.</li><li>Reports to Operation Managers.</li><li>Ensure that team members are fully briefed on new information within agreed time frame in order to effectively carry out their role.</li><li>Work closely with the Client to manage high priority cases.</li><li>Manage the productivity, performance and service quality of the Contact Centre team.</li><li>Work with respective stakeholders to ensure that all information is being cascaded accurately.</li><li>Provide feedback and recommendations.</li></ul><p><strong>Requirement </strong></p><ul><li>Higher Nitec/Diploma / A-Level / Degree</li><li>2-3 years of working experience in the related field.</li><li>Self-driven with excellent interpersonal and communication skills.</li><li>Proficient in Microsoft Office applications.</li><li>Ability to take the initiative, work independently, and accomplish tasks with minimal supervision.</li></ul><p>Interested applicants please send your resume to venessagoh@recruitexpress.com.sg</p><p>Venessa Goh Wee Ni</p><p>R24124686</p><p>Recruit Express Pte Ltd</p><p>EA License No: 99C4599</p><p>We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be contacted.</p>",
